title: Estadio Julián Tesucún
text: Estadio Julián Tesucún is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="San%20Jos%C3%A9%2C%20El%20Pet%C3%A9n">San José</a>, <a href="Guatemala">Guatemala</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches, on club level by <a href="Heredia%20Jaguares%20de%20Peten">Heredia Jaguares de Peten</a> of the <a href="Liga%20Nacional%20de%20F%C3%BAtbol%20de%20Guatemala">Liga Nacional de Fútbol de Guatemala</a>. The stadium has a capacity of 8,000 spectators.
